OL,3,C'More than half' of UK job losses
OL,4,Csince last Budget were in hospitality
OL,6,FResearch by lobby group UKHospitality
OL,7,Fshows more than half of all UK job
OL,8,Flosses this year have come from that
OL,9,Fsector. ITV News Reporter Mahatir
OL,10,FPasha explains
OL,12,FMore than half of all job losses in
OL,13,Fthe UK this year have come from the
OL,14,Fhospitality sector, according to an
OL,15,Findustry body.
OL,17,FUKHospitality has released figures
OL,18,Fshowing that of the 164,641 jobs lost
OL,19,Fsince the last Budget, in October
OL,20,F2024, almost 89,000 have been in the
OL,21,Fsector.
