OL,3,C'More than half' of UK job losses
OL,4,Csince last Budget were in hospitality
OL,6,FThat means hospitality - which
OL,7,Fincludes pubs, restaurants, hotels,
OL,8,Fentertainment venues and visitor
OL,9,Fattractions -accounted for 53% of all
OL,10,Fjob losses in that time.
OL,12,F"The number of job losses suffered in
OL,13,Fhospitality since the Budget is
OL,14,Fstaggering," said Kate Nicholls, Chair
OL,15,Fof UKHospitality.
OL,17,F"More than half of all job losses
OL,18,Fsince October occurring in hospitality
OL,19,Fis further evidence that our sector
OL,20,Fhas been by far the hardest hit by the
OL,21,FGovernment's regressive tax increases."
