OL,3,C'More than half' of UK job losses
OL,4,Csince last Budget were in hospitality
OL,6,FMs Nicholls said: "The sheer scale of
OL,7,Fcosts being placed upon hospitality
OL,8,Fhas forced businesses to take
OL,9,Fagonisingly tough decisions to cut
OL,10,Fjobs ` with part-time and flexible
OL,11,Froles often those most at risk."
OL,13,FShe called on the government to take
OL,14,Faction at the next Budget, which will
OL,15,Fannounced in October, by lowering
OL,16,Fbusiness rates, fixing National
OL,17,FInsurance Contributions and cutting
OL,18,FVAT.
